  "pages": [
    {
      "text": "Fifi the Fox has bright orange fur. One sunny morning she went out to play. She heard a gentle quack nearby.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F126bf36d-9457-4c94-a06d-0c58fe13fd35_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930537&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=hvUFHVGPAIy7Oy3WZiJCWmJVjWo%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifi peeked through the tall grass and saw Dottle the Duck splashing in a pond. 'Hello!' said Fifi, wagging her tail. Dottle smiled.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F87f8f022-075f-425f-b334-eb46c63ce25f_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930636&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=A1xy8i4AlnyOwzwUQpBASgNqjDw%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "The two new friends splashed and swam together. Fifi showed how to hide behind the lily pads. Dottle taught her how to float.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F4344fc7a-da4f-4e52-9844-41b333eb1282_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930658&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=uC3eshe%2Fuw1JqAxuHt7YoLRGUYY%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Later, Fifi found a juicy berry bush. She picked berries for Dottle, and Dottle shared his crisp breadcrumbs. They ate and giggled.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Ff002cfd0-e5d9-40fa-af88-535a1932d9fe_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930690&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=P%2F2j6Y8gXS1gc8rUtQhbGfNesVs%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "When the sky turned gray, a little rain fell. Fifi built a leaf umbrella for Dottle, and Dottle kept Fifi warm with a soft feather.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F32f12e3c-51d0-488c-b642-0b6d837cf66d_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930782&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=QCTctgKbziyaFss5W0isaZzdvaM%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "At sunset, they sat on a grassy hill. 'We are best friends,' said Fifi. Dottle quacked, 'Always!' They hugged and felt happy.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Ff8781b08-e951-4d5e-b448-a7ee1a2ea3c1_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930801&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=0ogv6VOS%2BdVYJDbQDgjq%2Bp7oLyA%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    }
